<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/821989-who-do-you-think-is-the-she-in-the">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Who do you think is the "She" in the title? Is it Rachel? Joanna Mays? Nicky? They all "knew" things and had secrets. I've gone back and forth with this question and I just can't figure out who the "She" is. Help me <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
